</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_229" id="113v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wan wir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan>, daz ir von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigisten
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. kunigs handel und den lewffen zu Beheim, wie <add>die yecz gestalt
                            sein</add>, wol wissen und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> mugt, so
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir uns bey disem botten
                        in guter <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> etwas
                                <expan>eygensch<ex>aft</ex></expan> davon
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet als vil ewch
                                <expan>füklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey, und uns darinn guten
                                <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiset. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>invocav<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
